    "Asta-ScholarQA-CS2.",
    "We use the official code foot_15 to evaluate our method and the baselines on Asta-ScholarQA-CS2.",
    "We compute rubric score, answer precision, citation precision and citation recall on the 100 test set questions using gemini-2.5-flash as the judge as detailed in Bragg et al. (2025).",
